  "body": "bazel option `--define google_grpc=disabled` has no effect when extension `envoy.tracers.opencensus` is included. \r\n\r\nThis was introduced in #9877. In the BUILD file for `opencensus_tracer_impl`, `//source/common/grpc:google_async_client_lib` was added as a dependency without wrapping it in `envoy_select_google_grpc`. This causes `google_grpc` to be included in the building.\r\n",
